HII regions. Accurate gas phase\nabundances are derived with the most robust results being Ne/S=7.5 and N/O=0.43\n(1.3 and 3.5 times the solar values, respectively).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2002 16:46:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
